   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>Subject One Hundred Eighteen THE LORD IS THE WAY Scripture: John 14:6 The way is the method To do anything we need a way.</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>In other words, we need a method.</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>To be saved, to be forgiven, to have eternal life, and to have God, all need the way, the method.</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>The Lord is the way The Lord said that He is the way; that is, He is the method.</S>
   <S PAR='5' RSNT='1' SNO='5'>Man needs a way to be saved, to be forgiven, to have eternal life and to have God.</S>
   <S PAR='6' RSNT='1' SNO='6'>The way is a living person, the Lord Jesus Himself.</S>
   <S PAR='7' RSNT='1' SNO='7'>Develop this in detail.</S>
   <S PAR='8' RSNT='1' SNO='8'>How can we have the Lord as the way?</S>
   <S PAR='9' RSNT='1' SNO='9'>We must confess that we ourselves have no way, no method.</S>
   <S PAR='10' RSNT='1' SNO='10'>Concerning the matters of sins being forgiven or of being saved or of having eternal life or of having God, men have no way, no method.</S>
   <S PAR='11' RSNT='1' SNO='11'>They can only sigh for having no way, no entrance.</S>
   <S PAR='12' RSNT='1' SNO='12'>We must confess that the Lord is the Son of God to be our Savior, our way, our method.</S>
   <S PAR='13' RSNT='1' SNO='13'>We must receive Him as our Savior, that is, receive Him as our way and as our means.</S>
   </TEXT>
